#. plugin:openlp:section:2:content
#: 
msgid "1. Install OpenLP 3.0 or later on your presentation computer\n"
"2. Enable the Remote plugin in OpenLP (Settings вҶ’ Configure OpenLP вҶ’ Plugins)\n"
"3. Enable the Alerts plugin in OpenLP for alert display support\n"
"4. Note the IP address of the OpenLP computer\n"
"5. Enter the server URL in the format: http://IP_ADDRESS:4316\n"
"6. If you've configured authentication in OpenLP, enter the username and password"
msgstr "1. Instala OpenLP 3.0 o posterior en tu ordenador de presentaciГіn\n"
"2. Activa el complemento Remoto en OpenLP (ConfiguraciГіn вҶ’ Configurar OpenLP вҶ’ Complementos)\n"
"3. Activa el complemento Alertas en OpenLP para soporte de visualizaciГіn de alertas\n"
"4. Anota la direcciГіn IP del ordenador OpenLP\n"
"5. Introduce la URL del servidor en el formato: http://DIRECCIГ“N_IP:4316\n"
"6. Si has configurado autenticaciГіn en OpenLP, introduce el nombre de usuario y contraseГұa"

